Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715}And now I'd like to ask Akimoto-sensei to lead the toast on behalf of all the authors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it frustrating that {\i1}KIYOSHI Knight{\i0} didn't win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I should accept the result gracefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your one-shot for the Tezuka Award was superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki Yuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like my music?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like most of your lyrics, but not the melodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to be straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you like me as a manga author?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sad face is lovely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to turn it into a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you turn it into a manga than a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:01:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That chief editor is pretty good, setting all this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm answering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got third place in initial polls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a rank like that, you can just go with the first storyline you made for chapter four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, should we really be satisfied with third place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't a first chapter usually get first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you got third in {\i1}Jack{\i0}, the top shounen magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hiramaru's {\i1}Otter 11{\i0}, which started two volumes before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got first place with its first chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, {\i1}Otter{\i0} had a great start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His second chapter got third place, and his third chapter got fourth place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arai-sensei's {\i1}Baked Cheese{\i0} started last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the first chapter got third place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd his second chapter do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, we can expect {\i1}TRAP {\i0}'s ranking to fall that much for the second chapter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the second chapter stays in the top ten, that's an accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, {\i1}TRAP {\i0}'s second and third chapters are well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a downer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some confidence in your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll tell us the rest at Friday's meeting, he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:03:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a good result, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we lost the best chance to claim the top spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko, I thought you'd be disappointed getting third but you seem fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get higher results.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm more relieved that the ranking isn't worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're aiming for the top spot with a long-running serialization, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next up is the decisive second chapter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we don't fall as much as {\i1}Cheese{\i0} did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miura is a bit too optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's brace ourselves for now. We can't expect to get any higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're still in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the deadline for chapter four is Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:05:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pen-in as much as I can and get it ready for the assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko, you're calm about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in rushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho said it was good in an e-mail, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guys get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any work to do here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, sorry for barging in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the first e-mail she's sent me since the photo book thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The second chapter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fight is coming up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I'll reply first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Detective TRAP{\i0} got a pretty good start, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, your style suits us much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than {\i1}Shounen{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Aoki meeting with the head editor of Jack SQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing an original work with KOOGY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay, Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you her editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A while ago, I asked her to polish up {\i1}hideout door{\i0} in preparation for the next serialization meeting, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The editorial department thinks the characters need to fight against something, shounen-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are already psychological struggles in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not exactly what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want punching and kicking, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, to put it simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave the drawing to Nakai, it'll work out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to change the content of the plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't think my story is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not willing to be flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Chief Editor Ibaraki of Jack SQ invited her to come over to his magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! Are you for real, Yuujirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Aoki's gonna start a serialization together with KOOGY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief editor of Jack SQ secretly introduced them at the New Year's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, Aoki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the deal has gone that far, she's probably not against it—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell my story to the readers no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My story isn't the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki, it's me, Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just speak from out here, so please listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true you're pairing up with KOOGY... no, Makaino?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? {\i1}hideout door{\i0} is a wonderful work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you submit it to the next serialization committee, it'll definitely pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your art can't convey my worldview or my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My art...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw so that it definitely satisfies you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll depict the world of Aoki Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Niizuma's assistant, so you can't take the time to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll practice without sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that as many times as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a park behind this apartment complex, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm done with work, I'll sit there and draw every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to see me from your window!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use every free moment to draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it. You're disturbing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I can draw art that satisfies you, I'll never stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless trying to convince a girl that drops you when she gets a taste of fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how much he risked on {\i1}hideout door{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai, didn't you leave for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just came back to get my supplies and the storyline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you talk to Miss Aoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I'll want a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to draw at Aoki's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until she's satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her place... you mean in her apartment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in her apartment. Outside of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this cold weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About manga, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the fourth chapter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first chapter got third place in the final results too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're off to a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are third in {\i1}Jack{\i0} ! Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just hoping we don't drop with the second chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are real downers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be happy you're in third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's aim for long-term serialization!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speaking of serialization...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KOOGY's started serializing with Jack SQ, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KOOGY?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more, he's partnering with Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, he called for a press conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's announced, there'll be a big fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with Jack SQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the top of the manga world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki and KOOGY?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a different publication, so it's really got nothing to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Nakai know already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko, let's try calling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's try probing Fukuda for info first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin!! Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that their first chapter was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}TRAP {\i0}'s serialization started!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Niizuma said to tell you it was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, there's something we're a bit concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that Aoki was partnering up with KOOGY...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you guys should worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that, just focus on your serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he told us not to worry, I'm even more worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I also think Nakai really likes Aoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Nakai can deal with a shock like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worried about it, I can't concentrate on writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think what Fukuda said is right. Being serialized is tougher than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we just have to move forward as best we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're worried, why not just call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't concentrate on your work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, it's Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um, is Nakai okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the past four days, every moment he hasn't been working,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai's been drawing in the park in front of Miss Aoki's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I don't really get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's drawing the manuscript at night where she can see him from her window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's February!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless! His hands will be frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get Miss Aoki back, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just seems like a stalker to me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting my future as a manga author on this work of Aoki's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't work, I'll be an assistant for life, or I'll go back home to my folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is he still drawing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be inconvenienced if you freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind and body are on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you've been watching me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work with you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely draw art that you can approve of!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to draw your world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to drag him back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but after seeing him, I don't have the heart to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he dies like this, he'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even if he dies"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dies!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, I get even more worried when you use words like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to quit worrying and focus on your serialization!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nakai is going to back to Aoki's place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. He's entrenched himself there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I shouldn't have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just worry about him all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to finish up the manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, she's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this Aoki person really didn't want him there, she'd call the police and they'd make him leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, she could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, should I contact the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, Nakai would curse you for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then, this woman doesn't call the police because she doesn't want him to hate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno... maybe she's just testing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in her heart, she still has doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it with your filthy hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, did you just call me filthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to touch my manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way more filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just spare my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this guy creeps me out.{not that he looks gross, but gives off an unpleasant feeeling to them}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave him and go have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could just peek inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that cold park, he drew something so perfectly..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our second chapter's in publication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think the polls will say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done all that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to wait for the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's more important to pen-in the fifth chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazy out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already starting to pile up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, the weather report said there'd be a snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowstorm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Niizuma's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing my own manga's plot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the park, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing pretty heavily here. How is it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's really coming down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's drawing manga in this snow, he'll die for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I had backup, I probably couldn't budge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai wants to prove he's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it before, but this is an ambition he'll die for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his decisi—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai is a member of your Fukuda team!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cant take this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him go home, by force if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in Mitaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get to the train station, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you draw in this weather, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freezing to death for that cold-hearted woman doesn't even make for a good joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting everything on {\i1}hideout door{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Aoki isn't bending or changing her opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may seem cold to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think with what I draw, I can turn it around into something with passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda, we're at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the ticket gate. {more like turnstile}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll come get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashirogi ran here because they're worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful, but it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to work with you once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll draw so that it definitely satisfies you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll depict your world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snow's getting thicker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, he'll really be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is he going to such lengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's just because he likes Aoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's more than just liking her, he's also in love with her work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his passion for manga is what's motivating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if he's got passion, if he hurts himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakai's my buddy in the Fukuda team!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely take him home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda? I already told you I won't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this park—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your art that was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't want to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was running from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write a story that'll be worthy of your art.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoki, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My art wasn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it? Guess there wasn't any point in you coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in and warm yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? C-Can I really, really come in-into... {this is a really broken sentence, he doesnt even finish the words}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just too creepy! I take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I only invited you in just as a working partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like our rival came back with a power-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm so sorry! So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Aoki to do her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Aoki Kou couldn't become the person who understood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a genius really is to be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, KOOGY will draw by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, Nakai got a fever and couldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda complained that he had trouble getting him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But now we can concentrate on {\i1}TRAP{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the results for the second chapter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our decisive second chapter...{shoubu as an adj...the decisive chapter, the chapter we wage battle with, the chapter of challenge, the chapter that's the real test....}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got eighth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our decisive second chapter got eighth place. {same deal as above}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.61,0:24:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will our next rank be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.16,0:24:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should support each other and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it slow! No hurry, no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.66,0:24:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You support yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.22,0:24:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Bakuman:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Support and Patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've begun to turn our dreams to reality!
