Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:28.28,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:34.54,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:39.84,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:46.34,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:52.97,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:59.31,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,751)\be1}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:08.03,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:14.29,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:21.04,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:27.30,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:33.18,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And rise back up again and again and again
